show.description: After becoming the world’s first living immortal, Adam returns to face his past and fulfill a promise—marrying Precy, the heiress of a powerful family. But when secrets, power games, and ancient rivalries resurface, Adam must choose between love and vengeance. Supreme Master is a high-stakes saga of martial might, buried pain, and the destiny of a warrior forged in fire. Watch Now.
